instructions:
for_the_dough:
in_a_mixing_bowl,combine_the_whole_wheat_flour_and_a_pinch_of_salt.
gradually_add_water_and_knead_the_mixture_into_a_smooth,pliable_dough._the_dough_should_not_be_too_sticky._cover_the_dough_and_let_it_rest_for_20-30_minutes.
for_the_potato_filling:
in_a_mixing_bowl,combine_the_mashed_potatoes,finely_chopped_onion,green_chilies,cumin_seeds,red_chili_powder,garam_masala,amchur_or_lemon_juice,fresh_coriander_leaves,and_salt._mix_well_to_make_the_potato_filling
